&lt;p data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;424&quot;&gt;Peak Energy is looking for a Facilities Engineer to join our team and execute tasks within and around&amp;nbsp; our Burlingame, CA facility supporting the physical plant, infrastructure, and overall company goals. This role will report to the Manager of Facilities, and the primary hours of operation will focus on supporting day to day prototype development activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;426&quot; data-end=&quot;773&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;In addition to supporting the Burlingame site, this individual will play a key role in supporting the build out, expansion, and operational readiness of Peak Energy’s future manufacturing facility in Sacramento. This is an exciting opportunity to help establish and scale facility operations in a fast paced, high growth manufacturing environment.&lt;/p&gt;
